      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "TCM believes \"internal conditions manifest externally\" - organ function directly reflects on the face. Natural beauty requires regulating the five organs, letting inner health shine outward." },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Heart & Beauty" },
      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "Heart governs blood vessels, heart Qi drives blood circulation, heart blood nourishes facial skin." },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Signs of Sufficient Heart Qi" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Rosy, glowing complexion", "Energetic, bright eyes", "Good sleep quality", "Happy, stable mood"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Signs of Heart Qi Deficiency" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Pale, dull complexion", "Palpitations, insomnia", "Low energy", "Prone to anxiety"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Heart-Nourishing Beauty Methods" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Diet: Red dates, longan, lotus seeds, lily bulb", "Acupoints: Shenmen, Neiguan", "Lifestyle: Stay calm, avoid excessive worry", "Tea: Rose tea, longan-red date tea"] },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Liver & Beauty" },
      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "Liver governs free flow, regulates Qi movement, liver blood nourishes tendons and eyes." },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Signs of Smooth Liver Qi" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Bright complexion, smooth skin", "Bright, spirited eyes", "Stable emotions, happy mood", "Normal menstruation"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Signs of Liver Stagnation" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Dull complexion, melasma", "Dry eyes", "Low mood or irritability", "Chest tightness, sighing"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Liver-Nourishing Beauty Methods" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Diet: Rose, chrysanthemum, goji, spinach", "Acupoints: Taichong, Qimen", "Lifestyle: Stay emotionally balanced, avoid late nights", "Tea: Rose tea, chrysanthemum-goji tea"] },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Spleen & Beauty" },
      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "Spleen governs transformation, is the source of Qi-Blood production, directly affects skin nutrition." },
